%2FuVPDzMZ.png&h=bf3aa72c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fASqeHp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfASqeHp.png&h=b6baca03&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jq38WVL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjq38WVL.png&h=c40770b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.yy藍扮黃post有成2000正皮,好多巴絲數臭yy藍扮黃,令到燈塔員工出黎爆料,表示yy一直都係奶共深藍,8月5號為左攞政治光環留住班中學生先扮野罷工,仲有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搞緊大灣區補習幫大陸蝗蟲落黎香港爭大學學位</span></span>,有巴打搵到好多財經新聞,<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">已fc yy係其中一個股東</span></span>,有唔少股份等等,燈塔員工巴打去yy個ig留言即被del comment block左滅聲,巴打留言已證實真係yy自己主動block ,個留言都搵唔到,之後再有學生留言質問yy點解搞大灣區補習再被del comment,<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果唔係身有屎,點解要滅聲</span></span>?最後仲要搵人警告爆料巴打,有圖自己睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dm7JLPM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDm7JLPM.png&h=29f39188&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c37tWWt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc37tWWt.png&h=298747cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2stpvgu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2stpvgu.png&h=9b2e42ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ppx5Y9R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPpx5Y9R.png&h=1e37343b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n達狗,yylam,ming仔,班奶共藍扮黃仆街撚屌幾時先收皮?港豬一邊屌一邊繼續送錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黃絲學生既你地,原來一直送錢俾一個滅聲,幫建制助選,要還警察公道既藍扮黃撚屌</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n光復香港!時代革命!<br />\n五大訴求!缺一不可!</span></span>"},{"pid":"e85647a7e7223ca86d038e06391463a25fd41232","tid":1739602,"ui